Model

Class User

  • java.lang.Object
    • Model.User
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class User
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    User class holds and manipulates information on all of the users in the system It can add and delete users, write all user information to memory (file/serilizaton), and other user manipulation and checks. It also holds the state of who is the current User in the system
    Author:
    Tom Raybould & Mike Tomkowich
    See Also:
